### Health Check
GET http://localhost:8084/sessions/health

###

### Get All Sessions
GET http://localhost:8084/sessions

###

### Create Session
POST http://localhost:8084/sessions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "playerId": 1,
  "maxPlayers": 4
}

###

### Get Session By Code
GET http://localhost:8084/sessions/REPLACE_SESSION_CODE

###

### Join Session
POST http://localhost:8084/sessions/REPLACE_SESSION_CODE/join
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "playerId": 1
}

###

### Resume Session
POST http://localhost:8084/sessions/REPLACE_SESSION_CODE/resume
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "playerId": 1
}

###

### Leave Session
POST http://localhost:8084/sessions/REPLACE_SESSION_CODE/leave
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "playerId": 1
}

###

### Heartbeat
PATCH http://localhost:8084/sessions/REPLACE_SESSION_CODE/players/1/heartbeat